  <p>
    Family members can stay updated of the visits after they occur through
    notifications sent through text and email.
  </p>
  <p>
    If they wish to get a closer look on the reports, they may choose to view
    reports through the dashboard.
  </p>
  <p>
    From the dashboard, families are able to adjust visitation details, send a
    gift to Rachel to be hand-delivered by the carrier, or add other family
    members to get notified about reports.
  </p>
